{"data": {"content": "看起来 tracking 参数需要是特定格式。让我先查看一下 run_code 工具的完整定义，特别是 tracking 参数的结构。", "model": "openrouter/tencent/hy3-preview:free", "tool_calls": [{"arguments": "{\"code\": \"import csv\\nimport json\\nfrom collections import defaultdict\\n\\n# 读取 sales.csv 并聚合 revenue\\nmonthly_revenue = defaultdict(int)\\n\\nwith open('sales.csv', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\\n    reader = csv.DictReader(f)\\n    for row in reader:\\n        month = row['month']\\n        revenue = int(row['revenue'])\\n        monthly_revenue[month] += revenue\\n\\n# 构建结果列表\\nsummary = [{\\\"month\\\": month, \\\"total_revenue\\\": total} for month, total in monthly_revenue.items()]\\n\\n# 写入 monthly_summary.json\\nwith open('monthly_summary.json', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\\n    json.dump(summary, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\\n\\n# 找出 top-1 月份（revenue 最高的月份）\\ntop_month = max(summary, key=lambda x: x['total_revenue'])\\n\\nprint(\\\"Monthly Summary:\\\", summary)\\nprint(\\\"Top-1 Month:\\\", top_month)\\n\", \"intent\": \"读取 sales.csv，按 month 聚合 revenue 总和，结果写入 monthly_summary.json，并打印 top-1 月份（revenue 最高的月份）。\", \"tracking\": \"{\\\"files\\\": {\\\"read\\\": [\\\"sales.csv\\\"], \\\"write\\\": [\\\"monthly_summary.json\\\"]}, \\\"variables\\\": [\\\"monthly_revenue\\\", \\\"summary\\\", \\\"top_month\\\"]}\"}", "id": "chatcmpl-tool-823e44c8e63c6c21", "name": "run_code"}]}, "msg": "response", "ts": "2026-05-07T00:34:53.454886+00:00"}
