result.errors:\\n    print(f\\\"ERROR: {test}\\\")\\n    print(traceback)\\n\\nif result.wasSuccessful():\\n    print(f\\\"\\\\n所有 {result.testsRun} 个测试都通过了！\\\")\\nelse:\\n    print(f\\\"\\\\n共运行 {result.testsRun} 个测试，失败 {len(result.failures)} 个，错误 {len(result.errors)} 个\\\")\", \"intent\": \"使用 unittest 模块直接运行 test_primes 测试并逐条列出结果\", \"tracking\": \"{\\\"files\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"primes.py\\\", \\\"mode\\\": \\\"read\\\"}, {\\\"path\\\": \\\"test_primes.py\\\", \\\"mode\\\": \\\"read\\\"}]}\"}", "name": "run_code"}, "id": "chatcmpl-tool-a5162746c9fdf8e0", "type": "function"}]}, {"content": "{\"action_id\": null, \"error_type\": \"invalid_arguments\", \"event_id\": \"e0fba25c5dac4dbbbb5725c7d6f4baf7\", \"kind\": \"ErrorObservation\", \"message\": \"Could not build CodeAction: 1 validation error for CodeAction\\ntracking\\n  Input should be a valid dictionary or instance of TrackingConfig [type=model_type, input_value='{\\\"files\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"pri....py\\\", \\\"mode\\\": \\\"read\\\"}]}', input_type=str]\\n    For further information visit https://errors.pydantic.dev/2.13/v/model_type\", \"success\": false, \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-07T16:39:47.951103Z\"}", "role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "chatcmpl-tool-a5162746c9fdf8e0"}, {"content": "`run_code` 的 tracking 参数一直有问题。让我直接解析之前 `run_command` 的输出结果，并整理成清晰的测试报告。从之前的输出可以看到所有测试都通过了，让我再检查一下文件列表确认都已创建：", "role": "assistant", "tool_calls": [{"function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "list_dir"}, "id": "chatcmpl-tool-bae9905f828452d6", "type": "function"}]}, {"content": "{\"action_id\": \"ca0cf69afcf7495c9e90b09a2b2450f9\", \"entries\": [{\"is_dir\": true, \"name\": \".code-agent\", \"size\": null}, {\"is_dir\": true, \"name\": \"__pycache__\", \"size\": null}, {\"is_dir\": false, \"name\": \"hello.py\", \"size\": 12}, {\"is_dir\": false, \"name\": \"monthly_summary.json\", \"size\": 168}, {\"is_dir\": false, \"name\": \"primes.py\", \"size\": 719}, {\"is_dir\": false, \"name\": \"process_sales.py\", \"size\": 79